                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-267-off1431 t18250915-267-cd1432"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2 s. 6 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-267-victim1346" type="victimName">
                        Barnard William 
